16 WHEREAS, this accomplished team achieved a remarkable 24-4 record and earned Lanier
17 County its first softball championship ever.
18 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
19 the members of this body congratulate the Lanier County High School Lady Bulldogs on
20 their victory at the GHSA Class A Division II State Softball Championship and extend best
21 wishes for their continued success.
22 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
23 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
24 Lanier County High School Lady Bulldogs.
